"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-brazilian-athlete-becomes-fifth-olympian-get-engaged-paris-2024-21397103\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Brazillian athlete Almir dos Santos became the fifth Olympian to get engaged atParis 2024after he proposed to his partner following the men's triple jump final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brazillian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999997707846, \"rank\": 2.29197698600677e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dos Santos, competing in his second Games, failed to trouble the podium in Friday's men's triply jump final, settling for an 11th-place finish at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain'sJordanDiaz triumphed with a jump of 17.86m, whilePortugal's Pedro Pichardo andItaly's Andy Diaz took silver and bronze respectively.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997881935902149, \"rank\": 0.00021082584266415142, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Pichardo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pedro Pichardo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Pichardo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Pichardo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Brazillian enjoyed a moment to remember after the final when he got down on one knee to propose to his stunned partner trackside who duly said yes.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brazillian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair then shared an embrace as the crowd cheered on the happy couple, with Dos Santos' proposal making him the fifth athlete to have got engaged so far in Paris.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943627245, \"rank\": 5.637287438532147e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the Games, the boyfriends of French sailors\\u00a0Sarah Steyaert and Charline Picon\\u00a0proposed to the pair after they won bronze in the skiff sailing.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.997794942841081, \"rank\": 0.001727196854176211, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Steyaert\", \"score\": 0.9999891812259167, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Steyaert\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Steyaert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Steyaert\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charline_Picon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charline Picon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charline_Picon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charline_Picon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, it was the turn of China's Liu Yuchen\\u00a0who proposed to his girlfriend and teammate Huang Yaqiongafter she won gold in the badminton mixed doubles final.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.992034745051791, \"rank\": 0.005954227942520926, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liu Yuchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A PROPOSAL AT THE ATHLETICS \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0092\\u008dCongratulations to Almir Dos Santos!#BBCOlympics#Paris2024#Olympicspic.twitter.com/YmiY2kRQXk  And just two days ago on Wednesday, France's Alice Finot broke the European record in the 3000m steeplechasebefore proposing to her partner in the stands.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Pernambuquinho\", \"score\": 0.8331330433059114, \"rank\": 0.19992100671706406, \"text\": \"Almir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Pernambuquinho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Almir_Pernambuquinho\"}, {\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997890018527797, \"rank\": 0.00013160736599348238, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"score\": 0.9782537304182337, \"rank\": 0.022229682244473907, \"text\": \"Alice\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.903307238765668e-17, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told myself that if I ran under nine minutes, knowing that nine is my lucky number and that we have been together for nine years, then I would propose,' Finot said, having crossed the line in eight minutes and 58.67seconds.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not like doing things like everyone else.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since he had not done it yet, I told myself that maybe it was up to me to do it.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, I gave a pin that I ran with to my boyfriend.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On it, it says: \\\"Love is in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943627245, \"rank\": 5.637287438532147e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's the one who always gives me strength and if I managed to get under nine minutes, that meant a lot.'\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Viral Turkish Olympic shooter explains the truth behind his iconic pose  ArrowMORE:Jake Paul reveals plan to compete for USA at the Olympics  ArrowMORE:Spain beat France despite goalkeeper's howler in wild Olympic football final  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2165, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jake Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997881935902149, \"rank\": 0.00021082584266415142, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_n